&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;highlight lasso&#34;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;gutter&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;code&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;Installing, this may &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;take&lt;/span&gt; a few minutes&lt;span class=&#34;params&#34;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;Please create a default UNIX user account. The username does &lt;span class=&#34;literal&#34;&gt;not&lt;/span&gt; need &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;to&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;match&lt;/span&gt; your Windows username.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;For more information visit: https:&lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;//aka.ms/wslusers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;Enter &lt;span class=&#34;literal&#34;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; UNIX username: weidows&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;literal&#34;&gt;New&lt;/span&gt; password:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;Retype &lt;span class=&#34;literal&#34;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; password:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;passwd: password updated successfully&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;Installation successful!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
