&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;office365: &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.office.com/?auth=2&#34;&gt;https://www.office.com/?auth=2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Weidows/Images/post/jFnAHYlXwmf4Ka1.png&#34; alt=&#34;20210704100827&#34; /&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
